{"tid":2179370,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"袁國勇：第三波疫情「慘勝一場」　料秋冬有第四波疫情","createTime":"2020-08-29T05:09:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-29T07:08:19.000Z","uid":20933,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"be2f0ca236a952aeeaecbcbea78a6b35a7d38d3c","tid":2179370,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T05:09:16.000Z","msg":"本港第三波新型冠狀病毒肺炎疫情近日稍有回落，港大微生物學系講座教授袁國勇今（29日）在港台節目《香港家書》表示，這一波疫情回落是「慘勝一場」，但他預計新冠疫情在秋冬季會再次惡化，並將迎來第四波疫情，強調港人絕不應鬆懈。<br />\n<br />\n袁國勇表示，新冠病毒是去年十二月開始爆發，證明大多數的呼吸道病毒在低溫和乾燥的天氣更容易傳播，因此推斷今年秋冬季將會有第四波疫情。他認爲香港在過去七個月的防疫經驗，有助應對秋冬疫情，但同時強調市民應盡量減少除下口罩聚餐或暢談。<br />\n<br />\n袁國勇稱，明白抗疫必須在公共衛生、經濟活動和市民的心理健康之間取得平衡，但市民要有心理準備，抗疫可能需持續多半年到一年，直到疫苗第三期臨床測試完成且證明安全有效，能大量生產及運到香港，生活才可回復正常。"},{"pid":"dd5bb041b29b22a5577ccdef548db0bdc4612110","tid":2179370,"uid":20933,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T05:09:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1546655-20200829.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1546655-20200829.htm&d=aJB%2Bq6ruafnyRbkwc%2FW5ZoPST22DtV%2BdF%2FIIxhOvvTQ%3D&h=b7f7fd03\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1546655-20200829.htm&h=25f1cafe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1546655-20200829.htm</a>"},{"pid":"f508933524544a64d1d9fa2d3d642758062d7629","tid":2179370,"uid":63108,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"dd5bb041b29b22a5577ccdef548db0bdc4612110","tid":2179370,"uid":20933,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T05:09:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1546655-20200829.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1546655-20200829.htm&d=aJB%2Bq6ruafnyRbkwc%2FW5ZoPST22DtV%2BdF%2FIIxhOvvTQ%3D&h=b7f7fd03\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1546655-20200829.htm&h=25f1cafe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1546655-20200829.htm</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T05:15:34.000Z","msg":"國安法幾時拉尻佢，成日恐嚇政苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbe3d123ce5a1b38b45d739f3fe181323dba69a5","tid":2179370,"uid":17504,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T05:16:57.000Z","msg":"搞咁多野，一定係想喺九月三十一號前放寬<br />\n十月一號某國國慶再邀請小雪嬸嬸跳幾場老舞<br />\n一定爆過新城勁爆<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"933fc418e3aa9f0f86c9f78cce5dbae80b3f5c8f","tid":2179370,"uid":165749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T05:18:53.000Z","msg":"一波接一波，波濤洶湧<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f829f199066f3d4075fcedc5473dfa73986b268a","tid":2179370,"uid":89752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T05:19:59.000Z","msg":"專家食屎(林鄭ver).jpg"},{"pid":"6afde9c8989b202eb1c585ec23f31eec414afaad","tid":2179370,"uid":274435,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T05:22:05.000Z","msg":"其實唔防疫由鳩佢爆先最有效<br />\n全世界有街出有得玩<br />\n以香港人咁撚怕死性格會自己控制自己"},{"pid":"abf80c9a92388af85b1b386f7935238bd2cbc826","tid":2179370,"uid":27416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T05:33:54.000Z","msg":"其實啲毒係咪牙勇控制架？"},{"pid":"1f5a5ca2bab28f0937f3a3c147b83744902cc39d","tid":2179370,"uid":65429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T05:34:30.000Z","msg":"希望係啦"},{"pid":"8759fe0fe82b5ca4b554bb58167a8c21f21b1df9","tid":2179370,"uid":76745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T07:08:19.000Z","msg":"又嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}